<TEXT>
<P>
A mother and son who operate a licensed foster-care and child day-care home in 
the Mira Mesa area of San Diego County have been arrested on suspicion of 
torturing children. Officials said Henri Mathis Dyson, 41, and her son, Harold 
Alexander Dyson, 24, were taken into custody after a 17-month-old boy in their 
