<P>
Procter &amp; Gamble Co. announced that it plans to remove palm oil from 
Crisco, its vegetable-based shortening product. The National Heart Savers Assn. 
of Omaha, Neb., which has been pressuring food manufacturers to alter product 
ingredients, applauded Procter &amp; Gamble's announcement. P&amp;G officials 
